      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BANG ON BONNIE (5) is going well, filling a minor placing two back then was a 6 length winner of an A10 at this track over 480m (29.59). Up a grade but in form now and is the testing material again. DRUMDOIT MILO (6) turned in a modest effort most recently when fifth at this track over 480m behind Swift Nyah (29.98) in an A9. Placed at his previous run. Expected to feature in the finish. FINAL SYDNEY (3) jumped from this trap last time and also the same course and distance to score an A10 win (29.54). Should be in this for a long way. SWIFT STYLE (4) is down a grade after finishing fifth two starts back at this track then was again out of the placings at his latest appearance in an A8 at this track over 480m (29.70). This easier so not to be underestimated.",
